ZH: 请问你的名字是什么？
EN: May I ask what your name is?

ZH: 请问你是哪国人？
EN: May I ask what nationality you are?

ZH: 请问今天几点开门？
EN: May I ask what time the store opens today?

ZH: 请问这里有没有厕所？
EN: May I ask if there is a bathroom here?

ZH: 请问这个菜单有什么特色菜？
EN: May I ask what the specialty dishes are on this menu?

ZH: 请问这本书多少钱？
EN: May I ask how much this book costs?

ZH: 请问这个地方怎么走？
EN: May I ask how to get to this place?

ZH: 请问你今天身体感觉怎么样？
EN: May I ask how you are feeling today?

ZH: 请问你最喜欢的颜色是什么？
EN: May I ask what your favorite color is?

ZH: 请问你有没有看到我的手机？
EN: May I ask if you have seen my phone?

ZH: 请问这个项目还在进行中吗？
EN: May I ask if this project is still ongoing?

ZH: 请问你对这个提议有什么看法？
EN: May I ask for your opinion on this proposal?

ZH: 请问你在哪儿工作？
EN: May I ask where you work?

ZH: 请问你是怎么学会说英文的？
EN: May I ask how you learned to speak English?

ZH: 请问今天的天气怎么样？
EN: May I ask what the weather is like today?

ZH: 请问你周末有什么计划？
EN: May I ask what your plans are for the weekend?

ZH: 请问你喜欢吃辣的食物吗？
EN: May I ask if you like spicy food?

ZH: 请问你从哪儿来？
EN: May I ask where you are from?

ZH: 请问你有没有参加过这个活动？
EN: May I ask if you have ever participated in this event?

ZH: 请问你认为如何解决这个问题？
EN: May I ask how you think we should solve this issue?
